trans-unit.source: JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter merges navigation back history and navigation forward history (as exposed by <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"></xref>) into a single, [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style navigation menu.
trans-unit.target: JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter mescla o histórico de navegação Voltar e o histórico de navegação direta (como expostos por <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref> ou <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"> </xref>) em uma única [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-menu de navegação de estilo.

trans-unit.source: Both <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> display navigation chrome that supports history navigation using the following mechanisms: - A button for navigating back one piece of content at a time.
trans-unit.target: Ambos <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>e <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>Exibir cromo de navegação que oferece suporte à navegação de histórico usando os seguintes mecanismos:-um botão de navegação de volta uma parte do conteúdo de cada vez.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: - A button for navigating forward one piece of content at a time.
trans-unit.target: -Um botão de navegação direta uma parte em um momento.

trans-unit.source: - An [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style drop-down list that shows: - A combined list of up to nine items in back navigation history and up to nine items in forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: -Um [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-lista suspensa de estilo que mostra:-itens de uma lista combinada de até nove no histórico de navegação e até nove itens no histórico de navegação de avanço.

trans-unit.source: - The position of the current piece of content with respect to both back and forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: -A posição do item atual do conteúdo em relação ao voltar e o histórico de navegação de avanço.

trans-unit.source: The navigation history is stored by both <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> in the following properties: **Back Navigation History**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: O histórico de navegação é armazenado pelo <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>nas seguintes propriedades: **novamente o histórico de navegação**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: **Forward Navigation History**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: **Encaminhar o histórico de navegação**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To create the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style drop-down list, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> use JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter to merge their individual back navigation history and forward navigation history into a single list of navigation history entries.
trans-unit.target: Para criar o [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-lista suspensa de estilo, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>usar JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter para mesclar seu histórico de navegação regressiva individuais e encaminhar o histórico de navegação em uma única lista de navegação de entradas de histórico.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: The resulting list contains up to nine entries from back navigation history and up to nine entries from forward navigation history, plus an entry for the current content.
trans-unit.target: A lista resultante contém até nove entradas de histórico de navegação e até nove entradas do histórico de navegação de avanço, além de uma entrada para o conteúdo atual.

trans-unit.source: If you create custom navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], and need to provide an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style drop-down list, you can use JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter to similar effect.
trans-unit.target: Se você criar navegação personalizados [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]e precisa fornecer um [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-lista suspensa de estilo, você pode usar JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter para efeito semelhante.

trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Merges two navigation history stacks.
trans-unit.target: Mescla duas pilhas de histórico de navegação.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, the navigation stacks are available from the following properties: - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A> For <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, the navigation stacks are available from the following properties: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A> <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A> The two passed navigation stacks are combined into a single navigation stack that contains up to nine items from each navigation stack plus the current item.
trans-unit.target: Para <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, as pilhas de navegação estão disponíveis as seguintes propriedades:- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A>para <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, as pilhas de navegação estão disponíveis as seguintes propriedades:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A><xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A>duas pilhas de navegação passado são combinadas em uma pilha de navegação única que contém itens até nove de cada pilha de navegação, além do item atual.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>
